{
  "stem": "4032.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But how they got away with-- because, of course, once the Polish army formed, he got back his big-- I never saw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe he would have helped me somehow a little, but never saw him anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he-- he was the head veterinarian doctor in the Polish army, because they were having a lot of horses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was a very big job, I mean, as a doctor, and as a general in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, wasn't a pleasant one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People, you know, they would-- it lasted about four or five weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And no facilities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So people-- the minute the train stopped, woman, man, children went down from, and just made right-- right there at-- at the train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] physiological necessities they did on the spot' there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The feeding wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it wasn't easy in those car boxes, in those-- to travel to Siberia such a far way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You survive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was a woman with two children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they got separated from her husband, and she was in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I tried to help her as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was with two little children, she-- but she went to work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she worked there, and she survived, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The kids survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I met them in Israel after the-- after-- they went out a little later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how they came to, but they-- they got to be in Israel after the war. '45 or '46, they came to Israel, where I was in '42 already in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
